      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How much does house cleaning cost in Birmingham, AL?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "House cleaning in Birmingham typically costs between $135 and $350, depending on home size, location, and service type. Standard cleaning for an average 3-bedroom home starts around $135-$200, while deep cleaning runs $225-$350. Premium areas like Mountain Brook and Vestavia Hills may see higher pricing due to larger homes and higher expectations."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How often should I have my house professionally cleaned?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Most families benefit from bi-weekly professional cleaning, which maintains cleanliness without excessive cost. Homes with pets, children, or high traffic may need weekly service, while singles or couples often find monthly cleaning sufficient."
